[30;1m82 | [0m[35m    At the beginning of each stage, the feature map size is halved (downsampled)[0m
[30;1m83 | [0m[35m    by a convolutional layer with strides=2, while the number of filters is[0m
[30;1m84 | [0m[35m    doubled. Within each stage, the layers have the same number filters and the[0m
[30;1m85 | [0m[35m    same number of filters.[0m
